{"tid":2359704,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼迷對 時間 數字 同 文字既認知係咪異於常人？","createTime":"2021-01-09T06:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T20:16:25.000Z","uid":42246,"like":32,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9f0782067b67cafc5e5543c17fc3b6b5504e53e1","tid":2359704,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:18:07.000Z","msg":"第一個自己話自己同曼迷唔係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkMynYE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkMynYE.png&h=8e4ad99f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qm25Yw0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQm25Yw0.png&h=2ed9332b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢自己10:45係我post留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g99cDxs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg99cDxs.png&h=ff9cd220&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後重好似想同曼迷割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1rEDy6a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1rEDy6a.png&h=4135cd69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Um1eRS6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUm1eRS6.png&h=d9c7923b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話我單野講足幾日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1GXQ9EM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1GXQ9EM.png&h=ef389867&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個陣個post未開夠24小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一日一個版本系列<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hf38Wmd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhf38Wmd.png&h=6aea3374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早幾日教人做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQtkNsT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQtkNsT.png&h=47d79ec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上係一個post 有咁多令人費解既言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n怕曼迷對文字認知有誤差<br />\n依個post討論緊 <br />\n曼迷對 時間 數字 同 文字 既誤差究竟有幾大？"},{"pid":"0281dc2a2f73ad6b6ddf9889f39ce55871893faf","tid":2359704,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:20:37.000Z","msg":"點同佢地討論<br />\n佢地認知同大家咁大誤差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c38890e9525819608d56811dfee22cc4e4e807c","tid":2359704,"uid":38189,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:25:14.000Z","msg":"明叔過緊嚟 你等等"},{"pid":"fce821ba163f49710a738b78a17d98565913327e","tid":2359704,"uid":12628,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:33:06.000Z","msg":"樓主本小氣簿習低左咁多資料，勤力👍🏻👍🏻"},{"pid":"bea95765a1a155cd959138637297f15da8cddf28","tid":2359704,"uid":42246,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c38890e9525819608d56811dfee22cc4e4e807c","tid":2359704,"uid":38189,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:25:14.000Z","msg":"明叔過緊嚟 你等等"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T06:34:41.000Z","msg":"個個post 明叔都柒左獲 <br />\n（唔cap了 太多圖 想睇去個個post#103）<br />\n成班入來拉低個post水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f874b4735f